$lang["pages_about_story_heading"]="The Story Behind Zipcube";
$lang["pages_about_story_text"]="Zipcube was founded by Guillaume Santacruz in the Google campus in London. Keen user of workspaces, He was wasting too much time contacting each venue individually, but also knew from experience that a lot of companies have extra space that they could rent. Thus, he decided to create a company which would combine an easy booking system with a very customisable interface for venue owners and individuals in order to share their unused spaces. The result of this is Zipcube. We are a diverse team of highly-qualified and enthusiastic people all aiming to turn private office and venue space into an easy to use online booking system. Our goal is to provide an accessible, easy to compare and affordable booking system for any space with a strong focus on quality and value-for-money. Our target is to be Europe's leading platform for booking workspaces, offices, meeting rooms and event spaces.";
